                                                <h3 class="card-title mb-0 text-heading fs-22 lh-15">
                                                    Property Description
                                                </h3>
                                                <p class="card-text mb-5">
                                                    Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur
                                                    adipiscing elit
